<br>
For example, level 1-10 kill little arachnites. Level 10-20 kill bigger arachnites in Myrkwood. Level 20-30 kill advanced arachnites in Spindehalla. Level 30-40 kill more arachniteas in Spindehalla. 41+ kill Super arachnites with capes in Jamt Mountains. <br>
<br>
