<br>
In EQ, you leveled to raid. Kill the big things - Big things = better loot = Better loot = brag rights on doing things first or a flamboyant looking character.<br>
<br>
In DAOC, you level to play quake with swords. It has no other point to it than that. Frankly because:<br>
<br>
1&gt; Keeps have no meaning. <br>
2&gt; Relics are not functional and have no meaning<br>
